column5: Probably the last big smallie of the season for me. She back swimming for the next lucky angler. Still hope to get out for some trout or muskie though.
Beaut. Gotta love that late season bass. One last memory of summer.
Nice fish! Fall can be rewarding and the lack of crowd's make it that more enjoyable!
Nice on jimmer, big fat fish.
Wow thats a pig smallie bud! Nice fish
Look at that belly!!!  The fish is  pretty thick too... Lol... Jk
Wow, nice catch!  Do you know the weight of it?
No weight, 22-23", actually caught it off the dock which really shocked me..
